document.discussion_title: West Brom nena inkhel tur Delhi Dynamos
document.topic_text: West Brom nena inkhel tur Delhi Dynamos Indian Super League club Delhi Dynamos chuan ISL khelh tur inbuatsaih nan West Brom chu September 3 khian The Hawthorns-ah an lenchilh dawn! Team pahnih inhmachhawn hun tur hi international break lai a nih avangin West Brom-in league match an khel dawn lo a, Delhi club hi an mikhual theih phah dawn a ni. Baggies leh Dynamos inhmachhawn tur hi Premier League club leh ISL club-in friendly match an khelh hmasak ber tur a ni dawn a, zan dar 7:30-ah team pahnih hi an inkhel dawn a ni. Delhi hian season hmasa khan Adil Nabi chu Baggies aṭang hian loan-in an lo hawh tawh a, club pahnih hi an thawkdun ṭha hle. Delhi Dynamos president Prashant Agarwal chuan, "Delhi Dynamos tan chuan Indian club zinga Premier League club tum hmasa ber kan ni tur hi inchhuanna tham a ni. Indian football-in hma a sawn zel a, he hun hi chhawr ṭangkaia hmasawn ve zel hi kan tum chu a ni," tiin West Brom nena an inkhel tur chungchang a sawi. Prashant Agarwal chuan West Brom nena an inkhel tur chu England-a Asian mite hipna tura ruahman an nih thu a sawi a, inkhel en man hi £5 (Rs. 439/-) a nih tur thu an puang nghal bawk. Share this Post
